  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The perimeter of an isosceles right triangle is <math alttext=\"18 plus 18 StartRoot 2 EndRoot\"><mrow>\n\t<mn>18</mn>\n\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mn>18</mn>\n\t\t<msqrt>\n\t\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t\t</msqrt>\n\t</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</math> inches. What is the length, in inches, of the hypotenuse of this triangle?</p>",
